cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with deep learning architectures and specifically focuses on convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the efficiency of the proposed architecture, which suggests that it could be relevant to the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper proposes a new strategy for binary operations, which could be relevant to the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
